in argentina  we are among the first real estate developers in argentina to report on a us stock market otcqb vino and our nonleveraged assets provide one of the few public vehicles to participate in the anticipated growth in value of argentina real estate algodon group is the only publicly traded luxury development brand with unleveraged real estate premium wines and luxury lifestyle assets currently focused on argentinaalgodon seeks to become the lvmh of south america with our initial collection of assets beginning in argentina due to its value proposition and current opportunities  algodon is an emerging luxury brand currently consisting of a collection of offerings that includes algodon fine wines algodon wine estates algodon wine  wellness resort algodon mansion and algodon extra virgin olive oil  our mission is to utilize the value inherent in our nonleveraged luxury assets and real estate as a base to roll up and acquire additional assets directly related to the future growth of our brand algodons winemakers work diligently towards the goal of our brand becoming synonymous with the best malbec and malbec blends in the world which we believe may significantly advance the value of the algodon luxury brand one of quality elegance and attention to detail  with our fines wines as our ambassador we identify and develop unique lifestyle properties vineyard operations and other real estate assets as well as luxury brands in argentina and may potentially expand in the future to other vital areas of south america and around the globe we are opportunistic investors with an entrepreneurial spirit and a contrarian investment philosophyour current luxury portfolio includes the vineyards and winery of algodon wine estates in san rafael mendoza which has received international accolades for algodon fine wines and which includes  acres  hectares of vines dating back to  as well as a  acre  hectare luxury real estate development with over  estate lots ranging from  to  acres and algodon wines  wellness resort a developing premier wine wellness culinary and sport resort that includes golf and tennis facilities an allsuite boutique hotel in buenos aires called algodon mansion located in the heart of the city’s luxury residential and embassy district and algodon olive oil the estate grown and awardwinning extra virgin olive oil that has been expertly blended to complement our winesinvesting in argentina before the crowd since  algodon wines  luxury development group inc is headquartered in new york city with offices in buenos aires and mendozawhy invest in argentina iconreport investing in argentina real estate iconnewsletter signup iconvisit our youtube channel current news  algodon wine estates malbec featured at restaurant gordon ramsay a michelin star restaurant in london  algodon wine estate’s malbec featured at michelin star restaurant the fat duck in west london  algodon fine wines partners with sherrylehmann  macri in us says that cambiemos will win elections in october  elsztain says argentina offers best opportunity in  years more algodon family history  algodon group  algodon wines  luxury development group search printshare linkedin twitter facebook google email algodon wine  luxury development group about business overview algodon brand history leadership partnerships investment strategy why algodon group why invest in argentina white paper brands algodon fine wines algodon mansion algodon wine estates algodon wine resort algodon olive oil ev wines wine collection old vines pima ocho  fincas malbec black label bonarda sparkling chenin blanc wine team news  events press releases media mentions industry news events newsletter investor relations overview shareholders’ club news  events leadership company information financial information sec filings corporate governance contact inquiries locations historyalgodon group is a delaware corporation originally formed in april  under the name investprivatecom inc the company later changed its name to diversified private equity corp in order to reflect its evolution from an internetbased brokerage firm into a retail brokerage firm focusing on the marketing of private offerings and a developer of international real estate projects continuing its growth and evolution the company has transitioned from a diversified private equity platform to a wine brand and a luxury real estate development company under the “algodon” brand and is now more widely recognized as “algodon” hence the company’s new name “algodon wines  luxury development group inc” or algodon group “algodon” which has received a significant amount of international press for its luxury hotel properties wines and real estate development is the name that most of the company’s investors and customers are familiar with and is likely the identity under which the company will receive press in the years aheadfrom the company’s inception its goal has consistently been to provide entrepreneurial and institutional investment opportunities to qualified or accredited investors to whom such opportunities historically were unavailable under current sec regulations there are millions of investors in the united states who can participate in the private equity products that algodon group offers and we believe that the investment products algodon group structures will be attractive to many qualified investorsthrough its whollyowned subsidiaries algodon group currently invests in develops and operates international real estate projects its whollyowned subsidiary dpec capital is a traditional retail securities brokerage firm which offers various nonpublic investment opportunities to qualified investors since approximately  dpec capital has concentrated its efforts on raising money for investment vehicles that were formed by its corporate affiliates many of which were in the biotech sector for corporate affiliates that were raising capital to invest in the various projects being developed in argentina or for other operating businesses under common control with algodon group vino key statistics  algodon wines  luxury development group inc financial ratios  marketwatch bulletin investor alert tokyo markets close in currencies europe markets london markets expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close algodon wines  luxury development group inc otc vino go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus algodon wines  luxury development group inc market closed  quotes are delayed by  min jul    pm vino quoteszigmandelayed   change   volume volume  quotes are delayed by  min quoteszigmandelayed previous close     change   day low day high    week low  week high   company description algodon wines  luxury development group inc engages in the real estate business its portfolio includes resorts hotels restaurants golf and tennis clubs and winemaking investments the company was founded by scott l mathis on april   and is headquartered in new york ny valuation pe current  efficiency revenueemployee  income per employee  receivables turnover  total asset turnover  liquidity current ratio  quick ratio  cash ratio  profitability gross margin  operating margin  pretax margin  net margin  return on assets  return on equity  return on total capital  return on invested capital  capital structure total debt to total equity  total debt to total capital  total debt to total assets  officers and executives name age officer since title mr scott l mathis   chairman president ceo  treasurer ms maria i echevarria   coo cfo secretary  compliance officer mr eric stear   managercorporate communications  marketing ms shari ferguson   controller mr julian h beale   independent director insider actions – purchase – sale  – number of transactions  date name shares transaction value  maria i echevarria c