and algodons winemakers work diligently towards the goal of our brand becoming synonymous with the best malbec and malbec blends in the world which we believe may significantly advance the value of the algodon luxury brand one of quality elegance and attention to detail  with our fines wines as our ambassador we identify and develop unique lifestyle properties vineyard operations and other real estate assets as well as luxury brands in argentina and may potentially expand in the future to other vital areas of south america and around the globe we are opportunistic investors with an entrepreneurial spirit and a contrarian investment philosophyour current luxury portfolio includes the vineyards and winery of algodon wine estates in san rafael mendoza which has received international accolades for algodon fine wines and which includes  acres  hectares of vines dating back to  as well as a  acre  hectare luxury real estate development with over  estate lots ranging from  to  acres and algodon wines  wellness resort a developing premier wine wellness culinary and sport resort that includes golf and tennis facilities an allsuite boutique hotel in buenos aires called algodon mansion located in the heart of the city’s luxury residential and embassy district and algodon olive oil the estate grown and awardwinning extra virgin olive oil that has been expertly blended to complement our winesinvesting in argentina before the crowd since  algodon wines  luxury development group inc is headquartered in new york city with offices in buenos aires and mendozawhy invest in argentina iconreport investing in argentina real estate iconnewsletter signup iconvisit our youtube channel current news  algodon wine estates malbec featured at restaurant gordon ramsay a michelin star restaurant in london  algodon wine estate’s malbec featured at michelin star restaurant the fat duck in west london  algodon fine wines partners with sherrylehmann  macri in us says that cambiemos will win elections